    "text": "<div>Given that : </div><div>a = _{{3*j}}_, b = _{{4*j}}_ and c =_{{5*j}}_</div><div>By Heron's Formula :</div><div>Area = \\(\\sqrt {s(s-a)(s-b)(s-c)}\\)</div><div>Where, s = \\({a+b+c}\\over 2\\) = \\( _{{3*j}}_+_{{4*j}}_+_{{5*j}}_\\over 2\\) =  _{{(3*j+4*j+5*j)/2}}_ </div><div>Therefore, applying Heron's Formula :</div><div>Area = \\(\\sqrt{_{{6*j}}_(_{{6*j}}_-_{{3*j}}_)(_{{6*j}}_-_{{4*j}}_)(_{{6*j}}_-_{{5*j}}_)}\\)</div><div>Area = \\(\\sqrt{_{{6*j}}_(_{{3*j}}_)(_{{2*j}}_)(_{{1*j}}_)}\\)</div><div>Area = \\(\\sqrt{_{{36*j*j*j*j}}_}\\)</div><div>Area = _{{6*j*j}}_</div>"
